{"tid":2477733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"越南女子因“醜”被拋棄，整容成功嫁給富商，今懷孕6月現原形？","createTime":"2021-04-06T13:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T02:17:46.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1dfd7d418048a11dff52230ee529cdb75b9f3c","tid":2477733,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"在這個&ldquo;顏值即正義&rdquo;的社會，美麗的外表毫無疑問會給人帶來很多便利，比如下面這位&ldquo;越南醜女&rdquo;，就因為一次成功的整容手術徹底改變了自己的人生，實現了&ldquo;逆風翻盤&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n越南醜女離婚後整成美女嫁富商，懷孕6個月現原形<br />\n  不知道大家還記不記得那位名為奎奇的越南女孩，4年前的她由於顏值實在太低，雖然已經結婚生子，但是最後還是因為外表問題和前夫分了手，受到了很大的打擊。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2Fd9f2c551p00qr4mws00zhc000ou00gic.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252Fd9f2c551p00qr4mws00zhc000ou00gic.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=df4d0772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  這位&ldquo;越南醜女&rdquo;奎奇被&ldquo;掃地出門&rdquo;回到了父母家中，吸取這次婚姻失敗的教訓後，奎奇做了一個十分大膽的決定&mdash;&mdash;去做整容手術。不過面臨整容手術的巨額收費，奎奇的父母很難承受這樣的經濟負擔，後來在奎奇的一再堅持下，老兩口還是藉錢才幫女兒整了容。<br />\n<br />\n  然而出乎每個人意料的是，整容手術極其成功，奎奇在做完手術後外表發生了翻天覆地的變化，簡直就像是換了一張臉，甚至之後還因為術後的高顏值徹底改變了人生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2Fed4a1182p00qr4mws00dfc000hj00elc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252Fed4a1182p00qr4mws00dfc000hj00elc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=03ac233b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  做完整容手術之後，奎奇很快找到了一份工作，並且在2019年12月時，奎奇結識了一位富商，很快墜入了愛河，並且在2020年12月成功踏入了婚姻殿堂，當時奎奇將結婚照分享在社交媒體上時，還曾經引來了很多網友的熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2Fb0927cb9p00qr4mws0157c000ov00k1c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252Fb0927cb9p00qr4mws0157c000ov00k1c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=e62ac783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  婚後奎奇很快就宣布自己懷上了寶寶，將已經14週的孕照曬在了社交媒體上。近日奎奇又在社交媒體上發布了自己孕期6個月的照片，不過顏值卻出現了急劇下滑，不僅整個人看上去都非常臃腫，臉部也是很不自然，即便化了妝也難以掩蓋一些外表上的缺陷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2F92f19d6ep00qr4mws00i5c000ow00iec.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252F92f19d6ep00qr4mws00i5c000ow00iec.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=d6587ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<br />\n  對於奎奇孕後的這種變化，網友們也是紛紛表達了自己的猜測，有網友認為奎奇這是明顯的&ldquo;整容後遺症&rdquo;，懷孕以後&ldquo;現了原形&rdquo;，還有的網友則覺得這樣的情況並不稀奇，很多女性在孕期時顏值都會出現大幅度的下滑。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2F9983b524p00qr4mws00n2c000my00gnc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252F9983b524p00qr4mws00n2c000my00gnc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=2176cc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孕期顏值大幅度下滑？正常現象<br />\n  不得不說奎奇這20多年的人生確實受到了太多顏值方面的影響，而之所以她會在孕後6個月出現顏值大幅度下滑的情況，其實是在情理之中的。<br />\n<br />\n  每個女人一生中都走在追求美麗的道路上，但是寶媽懷上寶寶以後，激素分泌會出現大幅度的變化，雌性激素分泌量大大增加，而奎奇本身之前又做過整容手術，在激素的影響下出現這樣的變化並不足為奇。<br />\n<br />\n  <img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2F498a42c6p00qr4mws00u7c000mw00hwc.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252F498a42c6p00qr4mws00u7c000mw00hwc.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=5c35813d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  而且其實很多寶媽懷上寶寶以後，孕期的顏值都會出現比較大的變化，尤其有的寶媽為了能夠為自己和寶寶提供充足的營養，還會在孕期中暴飲暴食，食量越來越大，從而導致身材走樣體重增加，顏值更是會&ldquo;一天一個樣&rdquo;，下降幅度更大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0406%2F3e036de1p00qr4mws00y5c000mz00h8c.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0406%252F3e036de1p00qr4mws00y5c000mz00h8c.png%26thumbnail%3D650x2147483647%26quality%3D80%26type%3Djpg&h=9d72d0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  比如奎奇分享的孕照，體重增加的就十分明顯，懷孕6個月後與懷孕14週時對比明顯&ldquo;圓了一圈&rdquo;，所以整個人的狀態看起來並不是太好。"},{"pid":"48cf7f6369a70d584b0e3e8be6b1eac395b723d7","tid":2477733,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"越南人啲素顏樣可以好極端<br />\n<br />\n可以好靚可以好肉酸"},{"pid":"38ce6e0d31cfa5b7a4efad82567c8c4096fb89af","tid":2477733,"uid":328316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:51:51.000Z","msg":"乜越南整容咁掂<br />\n點解唔見香港人話去越南整"},{"pid":"a0816e3ed38e1bc6d8a66e616f9cb5916a43a090","tid":2477733,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:57:02.000Z","msg":"整得幾好喎"},{"pid":"ed5fa55a6b06986e61488b22577ad7bfb3095b2c","tid":2477733,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"呢筆投資好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶黎幾百幾千倍回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4f8e42f3f3e84b40ce69063fa8753cb19524b1","tid":2477733,"uid":105201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"可能一開始塊面部份開刀部份打針<br />\n咁大肚無得打 啲針效力散晒咪開始走樣囉<br />\n生完減肥打返針又靚靚出嚟㗎啦"},{"pid":"ba96ab7f22b5af68036a73030caf86f89ff9efaa","tid":2477733,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6789fbec0e6e04a3fdef42f45615e24184c16ed8","tid":2477733,"uid":167956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T01:59:46.000Z","msg":"其實都係化妝問題姐<br />\n向來化妝都好似易容咁......"},{"pid":"2663eb1f77f3a3cb1e00040ea7dce4ce5859b2f6","tid":2477733,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48cf7f6369a70d584b0e3e8be6b1eac395b723d7","tid":2477733,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"越南人啲素顏樣可以好極端<br />\n<br />\n可以好靚可以好肉酸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:02:56.000Z","msg":"靚果d溝左法國種<br />\n其他係原生種"},{"pid":"7ccd1f649ed9256b670b395a1fd6973010d56d11","tid":2477733,"uid":234681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"48cf7f6369a70d584b0e3e8be6b1eac395b723d7","tid":2477733,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"越南人啲素顏樣可以好極端<br />\n<br />\n可以好靚可以好肉酸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"女人啲素顏樣可以好極端<br />\n<br />\n可以好靚可以好醜"},{"pid":"dd4da0a80223c73c6b5e3379958d3956f4730677","tid":2477733,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T02:17:46.000Z","msg":"整完好似SUNNY 條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}